Package: localsync
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-fastapi, python3-netifaces, python3-requests, python3-tabulate, python3-uvicorn, python3-watchdog, python3-zeroconf
Description: Local package synchronization and sharing tool
 LocalSync is a tool that allows you to share and synchronize packages
 across local networks. It provides a server that can share cached packages
 and a client that can discover and install packages from network peers.
 .
 Features:
  - Network discovery using mDNS/Bonjour
  - Package caching and sharing
  - Compatible package filtering by architecture
  - Web API for package management
  - Command-line interface for easy usage